  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "下取整等式",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "1. 嵌套 Floor 化简",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$\\big\\lfloor \\frac{\\lfloor x/a \\rfloor}{b} \\big\\rfloor = \\big\\lfloor \\frac{x}{a b} \\big\\rfloor \\quad (a,b>0 \\text{ 为整数})$$\n**作用**：将多层除法的下取整合并为一层，减少嵌套。\n**注意**：要求 $a,b$ 是正整数（实数时不一定成立）。",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "2. 带余除法的取整表示",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$n = d \\cdot \\left\\lfloor \\frac{n}{d} \\right\\rfloor + (n \\bmod d), \\quad 0 \\le n \\bmod d < d$$\n**作用**：建立整数除法商与余数之间的定量关系。\n**用法**：",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "heading": "下取整转换",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "一、 核心思想：消灭取整符号",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>万能公式：</strong>",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "对于 $\\lfloor \\frac{X}{Y} \\rfloor$，我们总是设：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$ X = q \\cdot Y + r $$\n其中约束条件是铁律：\n$$ 0 \\le r < Y $$",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "此时，原式中的 $\\lfloor \\frac{X}{Y} \\rfloor$ 直接变成了 $q$。",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "二、 标准解题两步走",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "假设你要解方程：$f(X, \\lfloor \\frac{X}{Y} \\rfloor) = C$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "heading": "1. <strong>设元、代入、化简</strong>",
              "level": 4,
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "令 $X = qY + r$（$0 \\le r \\le Y-1$）。",
                  "depth": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "把方程里所有的 $X$ 替换成 $qY+r$，所有的 $\\lfloor \\frac{X}{Y} \\rfloor$ 替换成 $q$。",
                  "depth": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "代入后求出 $r(q)$ 的函数。",
                  "depth": 2
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "heading": "2. <strong>定界</strong>",
              "level": 4,
              "blocks": [
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "利用 $r$ 的范围 $[0, Y-1]$，去卡 $q$ 的值。",
                  "depth": 2
                },
                {
                  "type": "p",
                  "html": "因为 $q$ 必须是整数，且必须满足 $r$ 的约束，通常这一步能直接求出唯一的 $q$。",
                  "depth": 2
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "三、 案例",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>题目</strong>：解方程 $x + \\lfloor \\frac{x}{3} \\rfloor = 100$。求整数 $x$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "1.  <strong>设元</strong>：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "设 $x = 3q + r$，其中 $0 \\le r < 3$（即 $r \\in \\{0, 1, 2\\}$），$\\lfloor \\frac{x}{3} \\rfloor$ 变成了 $q$。",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "2.  <strong>化简</strong>：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "代入方程：",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$ (3q + r) + q = 100 $$\n$$ 4q + r = 100 $$",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$ r = 100 - 4q $$",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "3.  <strong>定界</strong>：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "因为 $0 \\le r \\le 2$，所以：",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$ 0 \\le 100 - 4q \\le 2 $$\n解这个不等式：\n$$ -100 \\le -4q \\le -98 $$",
              "depth": 3
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$ 24.5 \\le q \\le 25 $$\n因为 $q$ 必须是整数，所以 **q = 25**。",
              "depth": 3
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
